sense.gloss: so-and-so, such and such, something (or other)
no, oh (not at all), please, there, there

sdata.j: ここにいる↑皆↑↓み|な↓に↑何↑↓なに|↓か↑言↑↓い↓いたいことはありますか。
sdata.e: Would you like to say something to everyone here?

sdata.j: 「ただいま、↑持↑↓も↓ち↑帰↑↓かえ↓り↑買↑↓か↓ってきた」「|なになに|？」「とんこつラーメンよ」「うわー、↑僕↑↓ぼく↓のことよくわかってるね！いただきまーす」
sdata.e: I'm back! I brought some takeout. "What'd you get?" "Some tonkotsu ramen." "Whoa, you know me so well! Well, let's eat already!"
